              <span id="reviewTextContainer2327730047" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14490470839045816067">A really interesting play! It asks what is normal, how are all of us grotesque, how do we use/abuse other people, how do we all make compromises in order to live in society, etc.<br/><br/>I&apos;ll need to read it a few more times to wrap my head around it all, but one reading was all it took to make me decide to teach this play next year in AP Lit. My students can help me figure it all out!</span>
  <span id="freeText14490470839045816067" style="display:none">A really interesting play! It asks what is normal, how are all of us grotesque, how do we use/abuse other people, how do we all make compromises in order to live in society, etc.<br /><br />I'll need to read it a few more times to wrap my head around it all, but one reading was all it took to make me decide to teach this play next year in AP Lit. My students can help me figure it all out!</span>
